                    <span>The issue is that most us find it difficult to have a small talk specially with strangers. <p>The conclusion is that if you take the risk (of rejection) and burden of making the small talk, you will reap the benefits.<p>The examples are good. I like it for the clarity and crispness. I am going to try the advise since it is not too difficult.</span>
                  
